component_text: computer can influence society, and people's lives have already been controlled by device
this modern device has been a major hindrance to some people
A study conducted by Mediabank shows that majority of Australian adults do not socialize with their families and friends as much as they used to
they spend almost nine hours a day dealing with computers as to produce efficient time in working
the idea that computers could be a help has been neglected
using computer can make people easier to complete their work
Businessmen, for example, use computer device to presentation or communication with their colleagues
Communication by feature-computer such as email and internet help busy businessmen to make deal with relation even in different country
This is due to using computer more efficient and, many workers cannot do more in work without computer
in era technology like this age, computer becomes important thing in human life
people cannot pass the day without stay in front of computer or using it
